### List nodes
GET http://localhost:8000/nodes
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Fetch telemetry for a node
GET http://localhost:8000/nodes/<node-id>/telemetry?from=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z&to=2024-01-02T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Fetch insights
GET http://localhost:8000/insights?nodeId=<node-id>&type=moisture_low
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Stream live data (SSE)
GET http://localhost:8000/live/<org-id>
Accept: text/event-stream
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Enqueue command
POST http://localhost:8000/commands
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

{
  "node_id": "<node-id>",
  "command": "irrigate",
  "payload": {
    "duration_minutes": 15
  }
}
